item.title: Prayer bpn12386 in Namibia
item.description: Ti Elotse, ≠gai-≠guite, é soutere, é !ná-!ná ti !nas ti ≠gaob dita. Elo geise ra !ná /gamirose ditere Sats ge Hoa-/geixa tsi a //kha. (Source category: Khoekhoegowab: ≠GAI-≠GUITE) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12386)
